    "faq_8dzUGE": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_e73Grk": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can Q-Renew help with hair changes during menopause?",
            "text": "<p>leading to finer strands, increased shedding, and reduced scalp coverage — a pattern that commonly presents as female pattern hair loss (androgenetic alopecia).</p><p>The Q-Renew LLLT Helmet is indicated for the promotion of hair growth in females with androgenetic alopecia who have Ludwig-Savin Classifications of I-II, which encompasses the thinning patterns many women experience during hormonal changes.</p><p>In a 16-week consumer use study with consistent use, participants showed visible improvements in hair thickness, density, and overall hair quality. Results may vary. If unsure whether the device is suitable for you, consult your healthcare provider.</p><p><strong>Do not use if pregnant or breastfeeding.</strong></p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_aJd9jV": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does the Qure Q-Renew LLLT Helmet work?",
            "text": "<p>The Q-Renew LLLT Helmet uses a combination of low-level laser therapy (LLLT) and red LED light therapy to help energize hair follicles and support healthier-looking, fuller hair. The lasers deliver focused light deeper into the scalp, while LEDs provide broader coverage</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_EAdrMB": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How often can I use this treatment?",
            "text": "<p>We recommend using the helmet 5-7 times per week for at least 16 weeks. After that, continue every other day to maintain results.</p><p>Each treatment lasts 12 minutes and ends automatically.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_WVdct6": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How quickly will I see the results?",
            "text": "<p>Visible changes take time. Most users should expect to use the helmet consistently for at least 3-6 months before noticing fuller, healthier-looking hair. Like any long-term treatment, consistency is key!</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_4xbifb": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it while it is charging?",
            "text": "<p>No. The helmet will not operate while charging. Always unplug before use.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_mkVbPN": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does it take to charge?",
            "text": "<p>A full charge takes about 4 hours. The helmet is powered by a rechargeable 3.7V, 5000mAh lithium-ion battery.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_mAjjJj": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is Q-Renew LLLT Helmet safe and FDA cleared?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, the Q-Renew LLLT Helmet is safe and FDA-cleared. It is included on the Australian Register of Therapeutic Goods (ARTG 522231) as a Class IIa medical device.<br/><br/>The Q-Renew LLLT Helmet is indicated for the promotion of hair growth in males who have Norwood-Hamilton classifications of IIa–V, and in females with androgenetic alopecia who have Ludwig-Savin Classifications of I–II, and in both, Fitzpatrick Classification of Skin Phototypes I to IV.<br/><br/>It features built-in safety sensors that only activate the lights when the device is properly positioned on your head. It will automatically pause if removed. The warmth is mild, with a maximum of 35°C (95°F).</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_M7qFY8": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Who is it not recommended for?",
            "text": "<p>Do not use this product if you are under 18, pregnant, breastfeeding, photosensitive, on light-sensitizing medications, prone to light-triggered headaches or seizures, or have open wounds or infections on the scalp.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_fgq9EN": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does Q-Renew LLLT Helmet come with a warranty?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, the Q-Renew LLLT Helmet comes with a 2 years of protection plus 1 extra year at no added cost. </p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        }
      },
